<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Library Management</title>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        /* Background image */
        background-image: url('https://www.giraffesocialmedia.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/trnava-university-sd8uJsf4XM4-unsplash.webp'); /* Replace with your image URL */
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); /* Semi-transparent white background */
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h2 {
        color: #007bff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: left;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    a:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to Library Management</h2>
        <p>Libraries play a crucial role in society by providing access to knowledge, promoting literacy, and fostering a love for learning. They serve as community hubs where people of all ages can explore books, access educational resources, and participate in cultural activities.</p>
        <a href="Home.jsp">Visit Home Page</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
